You think I'm delusional?

619
01:02:35,937 --> 01:02:36,847
Delusional?

620
01:02:37,697 --> 01:02:38,607
You are.

621
01:02:39,297 --> 01:02:42,289
Maybe all the hypnotism
has made me delusional.

622
01:02:43,377 --> 01:02:44,287
That's...

623
