637
01:03:51,497 --> 01:03:53,089
I'll apologise for him.

638
01:03:58,977 --> 01:04:02,014
Have you ever heard the saying,

639
01:04:02,257 --> 01:04:05,488
"Men are changed by events,
not events by men?"

640
01:04:09,577 --> 01:04:13,092
There's no present without the past.

641
01:04:14,457 --> 01:04:15,367
Thank you.

642
01:04:15,657 --> 01:04:16,612
What?

643
01:04:17,537 --> 01:04:18,447
Good speech.

644
01:04:21,257 --> 01:04:22,167
Where's Sam?

645
01:04:22,417 --> 01:04:24,612
He sent the two of us.

646
01:05:14,057 --> 01:05:14,967
Sam.

647
01:05:17,457 --> 01:05:18,492
Are you reading?

648
01:05:19,297 --> 01:05:20,525
Any recommendations?

649
01:05:20,777 --> 01:05:21,687
And you?

650
01:05:23,377 --> 01:05:25,845
How To Get Rich in One Day.
It's good.

651
01:05:26,097 --> 01:05:27,371
I don't need the money.

652
01:05:30,097 --> 01:05:32,895
I've helped you these last few years.

653
01:05:34,977 --> 01:05:36,171
You should speak first.

654
01:05:39,897 --> 01:05:42,457
You already know everything
that I know.

655
01:05:46,617 --> 01:05:48,016
Let's cut the crap.

656
01:05:49,257 --> 01:05:50,292
Will you help me?

657
01:05:51,977 --> 01:05:54,969
You help me, I help you.
We'll help each other.

658
01:05:55,737 --> 01:05:57,170
Good.

659
01:06:00,457 --> 01:06:01,776
What are you doing here?

660
01:06:02,337 --> 01:06:04,487
Me? I'm here...

661
